      "date": "2017-11-25 03:12:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-34vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/bb95c670-68f4-48bc-95f4-ccc4802f3f83). Ran 7 tests. No failures.",
